parameters: 【Masamune】The door is locked and won't open.
【Masamune】 The inside is dim, but it's normal...
【Tommy】 I wonder if I should use a light magic.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Did I get ahead of
you?

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's a cliché
reaction!

【Skeleton Head】 No, it's because the name was
long.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I am Sylvester von
Weisshwaik.

【Skeleton Head】 That's right, this is the dungeon
we found.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 The treasures in the
dungeon tend to be claimed quickly.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Do your best so that
you won't be surpassed by me.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 By the way, do you
know what's here?

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Of course, powerful
sealed magic must be sleeping here.

【Skeleton Head】 Damn it, if you're going to get
in the way, I'll kick you out right here!
Masamune!
【Masamune】 What do you mean, 'is it me'?

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Hmph, it's not like I
came unprepared, Paula.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Paula is my... well...
more like a friend... or an acquaintance!

【Paula】 Because it seems interesting, I'll help.
Please don't get in the way.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Hahaha... Well then,
if you'll excuse me.

【Skeleton Head】 Damn it, that dependent
bastard...

【Leon】 I wonder who that person was. They were
beautiful, but I've never seen them before.

【Leon】 I can't believe there was a girl that I
forgot to check. Huh.

【Masamune】 Looks like things have gotten
troublesome again...

【Masamune】 Most likely, that person completely
misunderstands the treasure here.

Will you forget everything and go outside?
(Progress will be reset)
